h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span>  <span>Text of Brugnone, checked against photograph.</span>  </span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2> translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\">  </p><p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>Preigomenia for Preimogenia, with similar metathesis in IG 14.546 (Katana), Syracusae and elsewhere.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> 36.0832 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a>  </li><li> Brugnone 1984-1985 249-250, pl.19 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002121\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002121</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
